EN: Please open the window and let fresh air in.

ZH: 能否打开电视？我想看新闻。
EN: Can you turn on the TV? I want to watch the news.

ZH: 昨天晚上我打开冰箱，发现没有食物了。
EN: Last night, when I opened the fridge, I found out there was no food.

ZH: 我打开手机，看到了一条重要短信。
EN: When I opened my phone, I saw an important message.

ZH: 他打开门，走进了会议室。
EN: He opened the door and walked into the conference room.

ZH: 他们打开车门，准备上车。
EN: They opened the car doors and prepared to get in.

ZH: 我尝试打开这个文件，但密码不正确。
EN: I tried to open this file, but the password is incorrect.

ZH: 请打开你的书本，我们要开始上课。
EN: Open your textbooks, please. We are going to start the class.

ZH: 我刚刚打开新游戏，非常好玩。
EN: I just opened a new game, it's so much fun.

ZH: 他急忙打开邮件，但没有收到回复。
EN: He hastily opened the email but didn't receive any reply.

ZH: 我给他发送了一封邮件，请他打开查看。
EN: I sent him an email, asking him to open and check it.

ZH: 我需要你帮我打开这个文件，但我忘了密码。
EN: I need your help to open this file, but I forgot the password.

ZH: 她打开了她的心扉，和我分享了所有的烦恼。
EN: She opened up her heart and shared all her worries with me.

